Well, the most common reason that the Client is not able to launch is because of missing or inadequate system permissions. It would be my recommendation to ensure all those are up to spec for League by working through our [permissions guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions)

Let me know if those steps caused any change.
